Who is Venus Williams?

Venus Williams is a famous tennis player from the United States. She was born on June 17, 1980, in Lynwood, California. Venus started playing tennis when she was very young. Her father, Richard Williams, taught her how to play. Venus has a younger sister named Serena, who is also a famous tennis player. Venus is very tall and strong, and she plays tennis very well.
